This is mxPlay 1.0.0, an audio media player for Atari 
TT030/Falcon030/Falcon060 computers.

Read about spreading conditions in the file doc/COPYING.

Read about different versions in the file doc/VERSIONS.

Read about plugins included in the file doc/PLUGINS.

Read about application's funcions in the file doc/html/using.htm.

Read about plugin API in the file doc/html/plg-api.htm.

Read about GEM API in the file doc/html/gem-api.htm.



Any questions, ideas, bugreports, ... welcomed.


Your mxPlay team.
